Rob Ruadh Sporran Clasp

(omhaigh bho https://www.nms.ac.uk/explore/collection-search-results/?item_id=20003 )

Tha an clasp sporran seo, mar a th air a chaitheamh le Rob Ruadh san nobhail aig Walter Scott, a falach domhaireachd marbhtach: ceithir dagaichean falaichte, a bhiodh gan lasadh mura biodh an sporran air fhosgladh gu ceart. S dcha gun do bhrosnaich seo earann anns an nobhail aig Sir Walter Scott, Rob Roy, far a bheil sporran a ghaisgich a fosgladh le bhith a toinneamh **one button in one direction, another in another... [when] the mouth of the purse... opened... a small steel pistol was concealed within the mounting... so that the weapon would... [when tampered with]... discharge.

D th ann an sporran?

Leis nach eil pcaidean anns an fhileadh traidiseanta, bidh an sporran na wallet airson nithean pearsanta sam bith eile a tha riatanach. Tha e gu re mhr mar thoradh air a phca crios meadhan-aoiseil Erpach cumanta. Ged a thinig pcaidean gu aodach san fharsaingeachd, lean an sporan air ann an Gidhealtachd na h-Alba air sgth gainnead nan goireasan sin ann an ideadh traidiseanta. Tha n sporran an crochadh fo n bhucall crios; agus thathas a danamh mran oidhirp gus an stoidhle agus an dealbhadh a mhaidseadh.

C a bh ann an Rob Ruadh MacGriogair?

Rugadh Rob Ruadh MacGriogair ann an Gleann Ghall, ann an Sruighlea, ann an 1671. Nas fhaide air adhart na bheatha dhfhs e ainmeil mar ruagaire (outlaw) no Scottish Robin Hood. Ach thisich a cheangal ri adhbhar nan Seumasach cho trth ri 1689, nuair a bha e 18 bliadhna a dhaois. An didh sin bha e an ss ann an aramach nan Seumasach ann an 1715 agus 1719.

B e neach-malairt cruidh cliiteach a bh ann an Rob Ruadh. A rir aithris bha e na mhirleach agus na fhear-ceannairc a bha a ruith racaid don buannachdail. Ann an 1712 chaidh cmhnant le Dic gu math cerr agus chaidh MacGriogair a thoirmeasg.

Chaochail e na dhachaigh ann am Balquidder, ann an Sruighlea, aig aois 63.

Rob Ruadh an uirsgeul

Thinig Rob Ruadh gu bhith na uirsgeul na bheatha fhin nuair a dhfhoillsich an t-ghdar Daniel Defoe cunntas ficseanail mu a bheatha, The Highland Rogue, ann an 1723. S dcha gun tug an fhill a bh air (his popularity) buaidh air a cho-dhnadh maitheanas a thoirt dha an didh a chur an grim ann an 1722.

Mheudaich a chli nuair a dhfhoillsich Sir Walter Scott an nobhail aige Rob Roy ann an 1817, agus tha e fill mhr air a bhith air an d chuid air an rd-rlar agus air an sgrion bhon uair sin.
